               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary>This manuscript contains the 16th-century <title xml:lang="sa">Laghuṭīkā</title> of <persName xml:lang="sa">Śivāgrayogin</persName>. It is a short commentary on the <title xml:lang="sa">Śivajñānabodha</title>, 12 verses that purport to be part of the <term xml:lang="sa">Śaivasiddhānta</term> <title xml:lang="sa">Rauravāgama</title>, although it does not appear in the published edition of the work. <persName xml:lang="sa">Śivāgrayogin</persName>'s commentary was previously published in <title>The Pandit</title> in 1907, and a more recent critical edition and translation by <persName>T. Ganesan</persName> was published in 2003. However, this manuscript contains an introductory paragraph at the beginning that does not appear in either printed publication.</summary>
                  
               <msItem defective="false"><title xml:lang="sa">Śivajñānabodhalaghuṭīkā</title><author xml:lang="sa">Śivāgrayogin</author><textLang mainLang="san"/><filiation><p>New Catalogus Catalogorum vol. 34, p. 181.</p></filiation><rubric xml:lang="sa"><milestone n="1r" facs="6" unit="folio"/>jñānānandam ayaṃ śuddham_ hariṇotpattikāraṇam | pāśavicchedakaṃ vande paśunām_ patim avyayam |</rubric><incipit xml:lang="sa">atha bhagavān_ śrīkarṇṇaḥ <lb n="2"/>parameśvaramayam | artthakāmamokṣeṣu paśunām_ puruṣārttheṣu param_ prayojanabhūtam_ mokṣan tat_sādhanabhūtam_ padārtthatrayavi<lb n="3"/>vekaś ca pṛṣṭo nandikeśvarāya samastāgamasāram_ rauravāgamāntargatam_ dvādaśasūtrātmakam_ śivajñānabodhākhyam_ śāstram upadi<lb n="4"/>ṣṭavān | tatrādau tāvat_ patipaśupāśeṣu pradhānabhūtatayā patipadārtthan nirūpayiṣyan · tat_bādhakam anumānādi<unclear>m_</unclear> sūtreṇa ni<lb n="5"/>badhnāti | strīpuṃnapuṃsakāditvādinā strīpuṃnapuṃsakāditvāt_  jagataḥ kāryyadarśanāt | asti karttā · saḥ hṛtvā · etat_ sṛjati · asmāt · pra<lb n="6"/>bhuḥ haraḥ jagataḥ karttāsti karyyadarśanāt | sa etac chṛtvā punas sṛjati asmāt | haraḥ prabhuḥ asyārtthaḥ kāryyadarśanā<lb n="7"/>t_ kāryyatvadarśanāt_ jagato mahīdharādeḥ ka<sic>rtta</sic>sti |</incipit><explicit xml:lang="sa"><milestone n="4v7" facs="13" unit="folio"/>śivajñānabodhe śāstre śaivārtthanirṇṇayam_ śaivārtthasya pūrvvoktasya <lb n="8"/>nirṇṇayam_ evam_ vidyāt_ uktenaiva prakāreṇa jānīyāt | na tu prakārāntareṇeti sarvvam avadātam |</explicit><finalRubric xml:lang="sa"><milestone n="4v8" facs="13" unit="folio"/><g ref="#pcl"/> iti śrīmadati<lb n="9"/>varṇṇāśramācāryyavaryyaśaivaparipālakaśivāgrayogiviracitāyām śivajñānabodhalaghuṭīkā sampūrṇṇam <g ref="#pcs"/></finalRubric><colophon xml:lang="sa"><lb n="10"/>haraḥ om <g ref="#pcl"/> śubham astu <g ref="#pcs"/></colophon></msItem></msContents>
